类 Person

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Person
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity(name="PERSON")
public class Person
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Person class is a model of the person. All records of person in this coursework, no matter who he/she is, are implemented as instances of this class.
